OL,3,CRayner pledges to 'make work pay' in
OL,4,CScotland ahead of visit to Glasgow
OL,6,FThe Deputy Prime Minister has pledged
OL,7,Fto "make work pay in Scotland", as
OL,8,Ffigures revealed parts of the country
OL,9,Fcould see the biggest boost to their
OL,10,Femployment than anywhere else in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of a visit to Glasgow
OL,14,Fon Thursday, Angela Rayner said the UK
OL,15,FGovernment's flagship Employment
OL,16,FRights Bill amounts to the "biggest
OL,17,Fupgrade to workers' rights in a
OL,18,Fgeneration".
