OL,3,CRayner pledges to 'make work pay' in
OL,4,CScotland ahead of visit to Glasgow
OL,6,FResearch from the UK Government has
OL,7,Ffound workers in central Scotland will
OL,8,Fsee the biggest boost to their wages
OL,9,Fas a result of the changes to workers'
OL,10,Frights.
OL,12,FAround 100,000 of the lowest-paid
OL,13,Femployees in Scotland are expected to
OL,14,Fbe affected by the changes, including
OL,15,Fthe ban on "exploitative" zero-hours
OL,16,Fcontracts.
