OL,6,FThe party said the change is needed as
OL,7,Fthe proportion of zero-hours contracts
OL,8,Fin Scotland has more than doubled
OL,9,Fsince 2013.
OL,11,FMs Rayner said the UK Government has
OL,12,Falready delivered the "biggest pay
OL,13,Fboost on record" after raising the
OL,14,Fminimum wage.
OL,16,FThat will result in an extra #1,400 a
OL,17,Fyear for eligible full-time workers
OL,18,Fand #2,500 a year for 18 to 20-year-
OL,19,Folds, whose wages are lower than their
OL,20,Folder counterparts.
