OL,6,FThe UK Government said parts of
OL,7,FScotland which have the highest rates
OL,8,Fof low pay would benefit the most from
OL,9,Fthese measures.
OL,11,FMs Rayner, who will later visit BAE
OL,12,FSystems in the city, said: "This is a
OL,13,FGovernment on the side of Scottish
OL,14,Fworkers. Our landmark plan to Make
OL,15,FWork Pay has already delivered one of
OL,16,Fthe biggest pay boosts on record ` and
OL,17,Fit is working people in Scotland who
OL,18,Fwill benefit the most.
