OL,4,CScotland ahead of visit to Glasgow
OL,6,F"Our Employment Rights Bill will make
OL,7,Fwork pay in Scotland and tackle the
OL,8,Finsecurity, inequality and low pay
OL,9,Fthat have held back workers and
OL,10,Fbusinesses for too long.
OL,12,F"We know there is business appetite to
OL,13,Fget going with our reforms and create
OL,14,Fa more modern, healthier and
OL,15,Fproductive workforce."
OL,17,FThe UK Government said its employment
OL,18,FBill also offer workers statutory sick
OL,19,Fpay from day one of illness alongside
OL,20,Fmaking flexible working the default.
