OL,6,FHowever, firms have raised concerns
OL,7,Fthat the changes will raise the cost
OL,8,Fof doing business even higher.
OL,10,FFashion retailer Next announced on
OL,11,FTuesday it will raise the price of its
OL,12,Fclothes by 1% to offset the cost of
OL,13,Fwage increases for its staff due to
OL,14,Fchanges by the Government.
OL,16,FIt said the rise in the minimum wage
OL,17,Falso came as the Chancellor hiked
OL,18,Fnational insurance for employers in
OL,19,Fher Budget.
