OL,6,FBut Scottish Trades Union Congress
OL,7,Fgeneral secretary Roz Foyer said: "The
OL,8,FEmployment Rights Bill, if fully
OL,9,Fenacted, can be the biggest upgrade in
OL,10,Fworkers' rights seen for a generation.
OL,12,F"Empowering workers to take a role in
OL,13,Fthe setting of shifts and working
OL,14,Fhours is a win-win, boosting worker
OL,15,Fsatisfaction and productivity.
OL,17,F"We look forward to working with the
OL,18,FUK Government, unions and employer
OL,19,Forganisations to ensure every worker
OL,20,Ffrom every nation has these same
OL,21,Frights and same sense of empowerment."
